title: Kelsey Healing Arts
author: Name
cleaned_text: Acupuncture is a time-honored practice of natural medicine. Its uses include pain management, stress reduction, and digestive & hormonal disorders. Cotter Kelsey is nationally certified and holds a doctorate in Acupuncture and Oriental Medicine. He has been in practice since 2011 and specializes in acupuncture for pain management, stress, and women's health. His clinic is located in Cumming, GA. Additional services include diet, exercise, and lifestyle counseling; tai chi, qigong, and meditation instruction.
